headline: US travel demand lags behind Europe & Asia, Booking CFO says
summary: Booking Holdings (BKNG) beat expectations in the latest quarter but warned that global uncertainty could dampen travel demand in the third quarter. Booking Holdings CFO Ewout Steenbergen joins Market Catalysts to discuss shifting travel trends, including softer US demand and a rise in European and Asian travel. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts here.

headline: Escape the Heat: Agoda's Summer 'Cool-cation' Destination Guide
summary: With unprecedented heatwaves sweeping across the globe this summer, South Korea is in the grip of its most intense heatwave in 117 years. Travelers are increasingly seeking cooler destinations to escape the hot and humid conditions. In response, digital travel platform Agoda has curated a list of refreshing 'cool-cation' destinations ideal for those looking to beat the heat.
